hopobject.name: Page
hopobject.body: I'll call back later blue green algae benefits side effects Had I watched Don Mancini’s The Curse of Chucky, latest in the seemingly unending Child’s Play killer-doll franchise, on DVD at home by myself, I might have found it tiresome, maybe even a bit dull. But at Frightfest, dialogue like “It’s a doll! What’s the worst that can happen?” and a splattery decapitation in enormous close-up brought the house down. Definitely one to watch with a like-minded audience.
